products.title: 1460 SMOOTH LEATHER LACE UP BOOTS
products.description: The 1460 is the original Dr. Martens boot. Its instantly recognizable DNA looks like this: 8 eyes, classic Dr. Martens Smooth leather, grooved sides, a heel-loop, yellow stitching, and a comfortable, air-cushioned sole. Now in more shades than ever. Born on 01.04.60. Named the 1460. Over six decades, our 8-eye work boot has become iconic Hardwearing and famously tough, our Smooth leather can be polished to shine or scuffed-up Our Goodyear-welted lines are heat-sealed at 700°C and reinforced with our signature welt stitch

products.title: 1461 SMOOTH LEATHER OXFORD SHOES
products.description: Docs Originals. In more shades than ever. Each season, we're enhancing our collection with classic colors from the DM's vault. Built from our traditional, durable Smooth leather. Fixed to a classic air-cushion sole with our signature Goodyear welt yellow stitches. Looking back and stepping forwards.

products.title: 3989 SMOOTH LEATHER BROGUE SHOES
products.description: First made in the mid-'60s, the unisex 3989 Brogue shoe features a unique combo of wingtip style with AirWair Bouncing Soles - a rebellious union of proper menswear and counterculture attitude.

products.title: ADRIAN YELLOW STITCH SMOOTH LEATHER TASSLE LOAFERS
products.description: Manufactured at the original Dr. Martens Cobbs Lane factory, The Adrian Tassel Loafer first hit the streets in 1980. And with a double tassel and kiltie fringe, the traditional unisex slip-on loafer has been a classic since day one.

products.title: POLLEY SMOOTH LEATHER MARY JANE SHOES
products.description: The Polley Mary Jane takes the grade school uniform look and turns up the edgy schoolgirl rebellion — all in our classic Smooth leather.

products.title: ADRIAN ARCADIA LEATHER TASSEL LOAFERS
products.description: The Tassel Loafer is a subcultural classic and is offered here in Arcadia leather which is a traditional grain leather, with its rub-off surface polished away to reveal an undertone. The classic tassel loafer in Burgundy Polished Smooth leather is made with Goodyear welt meaning the upper and sole are heat-sealed and sewn together. The Classic Dr. Martens air-cushioned sole is oil and fat resistant and has good abrasion and slip resistance.

products.title: ADRIAN SMOOTH LEATHER TASSEL LOAFERS
products.description: The Tassel Loafer is a subcultural classic and is offered here in our polished smooth leather, a twist on the classic Dr. Martens leather: durable, with a smooth and polished finish. The classic tassel loafer in Black Polished Smooth leather is made with Goodyear welt, meaning the upper and sole are heat-sealed and sewn together. Dr. Martens air-cushioned sole is oil and fat resistant and offers good abrasion and slip resistance.

products.title: VINTAGE 1460 QUILON LEATHER ANKLE BOOTS
products.description: The Made in England Vintage collection is handcrafted by our Northamptonshire factory cobblers using original construction techniques — plus Quilon, our rare, original specification Dr. Martens leather. Thick and corrected-grain with a matte finish, this leather only gets better with age.
